Lengthwise cut pea pods into slivers. In medium bowl toss together pea pods, carrots, tomatoes, green onions and basil. Set aside. In small bowl whisk together coconut milk, lime juice, sesame oil and red pepper. Drizzle over vegetables. Toss to coat. Cook vegan veggie burgers according to package directions. Serve hot burgers in focaccia, topped with vegetable mixture. ON THE GRILL: Preheat grill. Use a food thermometer to be sure patties reach minimum internal temperature of 160 degrees F.